name: Malaysian Virgin Weave - Straight or Wavy
description: Virgin hair is the finest quality premium human hair available. Each bundle is 3.5 - 4 ounces and has been collected from one donor. All cuticles are in tact, and you will notice each piece has a natural taper at the end. All Virgin hair has undergone a stringent quality assurance process to ensure it is free of imperfections. Virgin hair is available in a natural 1B, and will last up to a year with proper care.
